{
  "stem": "10905.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had a factory called [NON-ENGLISH], means Brothers Goldner-- three brothers who had the largest, if not the only, factory that had-- that produced sinks, bathtubs, ice boxes, refrigerators for all of that area of Yugoslavia and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The factory itself had its own rail siding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was a 15-bed infirmary for the workers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My grandfather was a very, very progressive man as far as that's concerned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the-- the family lived in the same place where the factory was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was a main entrance with an archway from the street, and the two brothers lived on either side of the archway.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The various families lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was connected in the middle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I recall that very-- very clearly because that was a huge hallway, and we'd have maybe 40 or 50 or 60 people on high holidays for dinners.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And towards the back was the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then, of course, the rail siding, et cetera, et cetera, what have you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] In Belgrade, when we lived in Belgrade, we lived in a house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was a corner house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My father was a very successful pediatrician.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I know we lived-- my dad had his office, similar to where I have mine now, on the ground floor of the building where we lived.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we lived several floors up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Whether it was the third or fourth or fifth floor, I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we were well off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I had my room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My sister had my-- her own room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had a cook.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had a maid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we lived rather well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And everything was just hunky-dory until the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My dad had been mobilized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he was in the Army, Yugoslav Army, when the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they came early.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
